name: ZHIVAGO's country house view wrapping paper
description:
An innovative concept stationery collection based on director David Lean's 1965 movie adaptation of the novel 'Doctor Zhivago'

The midnight blue and white tree design, inspired by the view from Zhivago's country house, is screen printed on a series of greeting cards, notebooks and wrapping papers.

To customise your present and products, choose from a series of matching stickers which fit perfectly within the circles of the tree designs.

ZHIVAGO wrapping paper sheet

50x70cm

Midnight blue & white

Screen printed by hand in East London onto recycled paper

*Sticker set sold separately
